仕宏成立5周年，是次拍賣會搜羅了一系列多元化且卓爾不凡的雅逸珍品，涵蓋茶道‧香道‧花道、古董級普洱及佳茗、補品和佳釀、及茅台珍釀。成交詳情可按這裏。\n\n仕宏拍賣將會繼續為收藏家搜羅更多不同的珍貴拍品，在下一屆拍賣會舉辦前，請繼續留意仕宏拍賣網頁、Facebook及微信的更新。 '), ('11', '個人隱私', 'privacy', '', '<p>coming soon</p><div class=\"t_and_c_title\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 26, 29);\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Auction:</span></span></div><div class=\"t_and_c_info\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">The auction to be held on 28 May 2017&nbsp;at The Residence, Mezzanine Level, Grand Hyatt&nbsp;Hong Kong, 1 Harbour Road, Wan Chai, Hong Kong.</div><div class=\"t_and_c_info\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp;</div><div class=\"t_and_c_title\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 26, 29);\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Lot(s):</span></span></div><div class=\"t_and_c_info\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">Any item consigned to L&amp;H Auction that to be available to sales at the Auction. A lot can be an individual item or items comprised in a group of two or more items offered for sale as one lot.</div><div class=\"t_and_c_info\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp;</div><div class=\"t_and_c_title\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 26, 29);\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Reserve Price:</span></span></div><div class=\"t_and_c_info\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">The minimum price that a Lot may be sold whether by auction or by private treaty.</div><div class=\"t_and_c_info\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp;</div><div class=\"t_and_c_title\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 26, 29);\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Consignor:</span></span></div><div class=\"t_and_c_info\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">A person or a company consign the Lot(s) to be sold in the Auction.</div><div class=\"t_and_c_info\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp;</div><div class=\"t_and_c_title\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 26, 29);\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Buyer:</span></span></div><div class=\"t_and_c_info\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">The party, a person or a company, to whom a Lot is knocked down by the Auctioneer.</div><div class=\"t_and_c_info\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp;</div><div class=\"t_and_c_title\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 26, 29);\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Auctioneer:</span></span></div><div class=\"t_and_c_info\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">The person represents L&amp;H Auction conducting the sale in the Auction.</div><p style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp;</p>', '<p>coming soon</p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(142, 26, 29);\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">拍賣會:</span></span><br style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">於2017年5月28日假香港灣仔港灣道一號香港君悅酒店M層君寓廳 The Residence&nbsp;舉行的拍賣會。</span><br style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><br style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(142, 26, 29);\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">拍品:</span></span><br style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">所有寄售到L&amp;H Auction並於是次拍賣會中拍賣的貨品。每件拍品可為獨立貨品，或以兩件或以上的貨品組合而成。</span><br style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><br style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(142, 26, 29);\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">保留價:</span></span><br style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">是由L&amp;H Auction及寄售人為每件拍品所設定的一個不公開的最低售價。</span><br style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><br style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(142, 26, 29);\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">寄售人:</span></span><br style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">於是次拍賣會中寄售拍品的物主或物主代理人，或保管物品之公司或委託人。</span><br style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><br style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(142, 26, 29);\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">買家:</span></span><br style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">以拍賣官的落槌價購入拍品的任何單位、個人或公司。</span><br style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><br style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(142, 26, 29);\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">拍賣官:</span></span><br style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">是次拍賣會上代表L&amp;H Auction拍賣物品之專業人員。</span></p>', '', ''), ('10', '條款及細則', 'Terms and Condition of Sale ', '', '<div class=\"tnc\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family: Arial;\"><h3><a href=\"./notice_to_bidders\" _fcksavedurl=\"./notice_to_bidders\"><em><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Click here to read Notice to Bidders</span></span></em></a></h3><p>&nbsp;Please refer to Chinese site.</p></div><p style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp;</p>', '<h3 style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><a href=\"./notice_to_bidders\" _fcksavedurl=\"./notice_to_bidders\"><em><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 0, 0);\">按此閱讀競投者通知書</span></em></a></h3><p style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">以下協議適用於仕宏拍賣有限公司（L&amp;H Auction Co., Ltd.,&nbsp; 簡稱 “L&amp;H Auction“） 舉行的所有拍賣會。<br>L&amp;H Auction、拍品寄售人及買家均受此協議約束。<br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 26, 29);\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">1.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;買家佣金</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 40px; font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 26, 29);\">（只適用於「茶道、香道、花器專場」及「補品及佳釀專場」）</span></span></p><p style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">參與現場競投、電話競投、委託競投的買家，在拍賣成交後，以現金，支票， 銀行轉帳或銀行匯款結帳，須向L&amp;H Auction 支付成交價的18%作為買家佣金；以EPS結帳，買家須支付額外1%手續費；以信用卡結帳，買家須支付額外2%手續費。</span></p><div style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp;</div><div style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">網上競投者，在拍賣成交後，則須以現金，支票，銀行轉帳或銀行匯款結帳。 經“易拍全球”將額外收取3%手續費；經“LiveAuctioneers”將額外收取5%手續費。</div><p style=\"margin-left: 40px; font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 26, 29);\">（只適用於「古董級普洱茶及佳茗專場」）</span></span></p><p style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">參與現場競投、電話競投、委託競投的買家，在拍賣成交後，以現金，支票， 銀行轉帳或銀行匯款結帳，須向L&amp;H Auction 支付成交價的18%作為買家佣金；以EPS結帳，買家須支付額外1%手續費；以信用卡結帳，買家須支付額外2%手續費。</p><p style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">網上競投者，在拍賣成交後，則須以現金，支票，銀行轉帳或銀行匯款結帳。 經“易拍全球”將額外收取3%手續費；經“LiveAuctioneers”將額外收取5%手續費。</span></p><p style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 13px;\">成交金額為200萬至400萬之間，買家佣金可獲減免2%以作優惠。</span><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 13px;\">成交金額為400萬至600萬之間，買家佣金可獲減免4%以作優惠。<br></span><span style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 13px;\">成交金額為600萬或以上，買家佣金可獲減免6%以作優惠。</span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 40px; font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 26, 29);\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">（</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">只適用於「中國書畫專場」及「中國書畫(二)」</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">）</span></span></p><p style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">參與現場競投、電話競投、委託競投的買家，在拍賣成交後，以現金，支票， 銀行轉帳或銀行匯款結帳，須向L&amp;H Auction 支付成交價的15%作為買家佣金；以EPS結帳，買家須支付額外1%手續費；以信用卡結帳，買家須支付額外2%手續費。</span></p><div style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp;</div><div style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">網上競投者，在拍賣成交後，則須以現金，支票，銀行轉帳或銀行匯款結帳。 經“易拍全球”將額外收取3%手續費；經“LiveAuctioneers”將額外收取5%手續費。</div><div style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp;</div><p style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><u><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">成功競投者於拍賣會當天起7個工作天內付清款項，均可減免3%買家佣金以作優惠。</span><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 26, 29); font-size: 13.3333px;\">（</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">適用於所有專場</span><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 26, 29); font-size: 13.3333px;\">）</span>。<br></span></u><br><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 26, 29);\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">2.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;保證金</span></span></p><div style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">參與「中國書畫專場」及「中國書畫(二)」的競投者必須向L&amp;H Auction繳付<u><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">港幣5萬元正</span></u>作保證金。競投者如欲透過電話、網絡或委託形式參與拍賣，則須在<u><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">拍賣會舉行的10個工作天前</span></u>遞交申請書及保證金。付款方式可以透過現金、支票、銀行轉帳或銀行匯款，L&amp;H Auction確認收到申請書及保證金後，將以電郵方式回覆競投者作確認。逾期遞交申請書及保證金將被視為無效。</div><div style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp;</div><div style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">如欲參與現場競投的競投者，則須在該場拍賣會開始前的1小時內到登記處繳付保證金及領取投標牌，保證金只接受以現金或信用卡的方式繳付。如競投者成功競投任何拍品，保證金可於「中國書畫專場」及「中國書畫(二)」完結後可用作抵扣相關款項，餘款將於3個工作天內退款。</div><div style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp;</div><div style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">如競投者未能成功競投任何拍品，若以現金或信用卡繳付保證金可於該場拍賣會後當天全數退款，若以支票、<span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">銀行轉帳或銀行匯款將於拍賣會後3個工作天內全數退款。</span></div><p style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><br><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 26, 29);\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">3.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;拍賣品成色及圖錄</span></span></p><p style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">所有拍品均以其現況出售。不可退貨，所有銷售均為一錘定音。拍賣品圖錄中的文字介紹、估價、圖片及以其他形式的影像製品和宣傳品僅供參考，並不代表</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">L&amp;H Auction&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">就拍賣品之真實性、價值、色調、品質及瑕疵（如有</span><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif; background: rgb(252, 252, 252);\">）</span><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">等作擔保。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">L&amp;H Auction&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">可於拍賣前對上述之介紹及評價作出修訂，並無需對其中的不準確或遺漏之處負上責任。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">L&amp;H Auction</span><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">建議買家在拍賣前親自前來鑑定拍品，自行判斷，以瞭解拍品狀況。</span></p><p style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">如拍賣品在圖錄及其他形式的圖示、影像製品和宣傳品中，因印刷或攝影技術等原因導致與實物的色調、顏色、層次、形態等存在誤差，則以實物為準。</span></p><p style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><br><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 26, 29);\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">4.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;估價</span></span><br>本圖錄中所有價格均以港元（ “$” ）顯示。估價並非指該拍品自身應有的市場價值或最終價格。拍品估價只供參考，在拍賣會開始前，L&amp;H Auction 可對估價進行調整。<br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 26, 29);\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">5.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;預展</span></span><br>L&amp;H Auction會將所有拍品於拍賣前進行公眾預展， L&amp;H Auction 建議買家在預展日親自前來鑑定拍品及了解其狀況；買家需對競投拍品的行為負責，不應依賴圖錄中的說明以及其他形式的影像製品和宣傳品之陳述作出決定。<br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 26, 29);\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">6.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;撤回拍品</span></span><br>L&amp;H Auction有權於拍賣前撤回任何拍品。<br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 26, 29);\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">7.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;競投、拒絕和保留價</span></span><br>競投人競投成功後，即成為該拍品的買家。L&amp;H Auction 及拍賣官可以拒絕任何視為出價過低的公開競投並撤回拍品。成交價並不包括買家佣金及其他附加費用，付款詳情可細閱本條款中第12條。<br><br>每件拍品都設有一個保留價。在競投過程中，拍賣官可以拒絕任何低於保留價的競投。<br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 26, 29);\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">8.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;透過傳真、電話或電郵的委託競投</span></span><br>買家可委託L&amp;H Auction 進行競投。圖錄、申請表及競投委託書等所需文件可從官方網址下載 :&nbsp; www.lhauction.com.hk。</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0.15pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">所有競投將按照拍賣條款及競投者出價，盡可能以最低價格執行。請注意，為買家的利益起見，敬請所有競投者盡早交回委託表格。如有兩位或以上的競投者就同一件拍品開出相同價格，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">L&amp;H Auction&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">將以先到先得的原則處理。電話競投者會於拍賣會開始前，收到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">L&amp;H Auction&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">的致電，但本公司不能保證所有電話均可以成功接通，電話競投者須承擔風險。委託競投除「中國書畫專場」及「中國書畫</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">二</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">」外，所有委託競投表格必須在本拍賣會開始前</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">48</span><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">小時內遞交。委託競投「中國書畫專場」及「中國書畫</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">二</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">」的買家請細閱本條款中第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">條。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0.15pt;\">如未能及時提供所需資料，或在競投過程中出現因競投者疏忽而引致的任何過失，L&amp;H Auction將不會為此承擔任何責任。<br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 26, 29);\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">9.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;網上競投</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0.15pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">有關網上競投登記及其他相關事宜，可參閱</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">www.lhauction.com.hk/tc/buy.php&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">或瀏覽</span>&nbsp;<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">“</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">易拍全球</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">”</span><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">及</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">“LiveAuctioneers”</span><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">。網上競投者必須提前透過網站進行登記及通過</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">L&amp;H Auction&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">的審批，方可進行網上競投。買家須支付成交價及買家佣金，詳情請細閱本條款中第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">條。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0.15pt;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 26, 29);\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">10.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;拍賣成功</span></span><br>最高競投價經拍賣官落槌，或以其他公開表示買定的方式，即表明該競投人競投成功，成為該拍品的買家，亦表明買賣雙方之間已訂立拍賣合約。<br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 26, 29);\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">11.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;擁有權和風險</span></span><br>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;買家須全額繳付成交價及買家佣金，並經由L&amp;H Auction確定款項被接納後，買家可獲得該拍賣品的擁有權。同時，有關該拍品的風險亦會轉移至買家。<br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 26, 29);\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">12.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;付款及賠償條款</span></span></p><div style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">所有款項須於拍賣會後的15個工作天內全數繳付，可採用以下任何一種付款方式，以港幣支付拍品的成交價及買家佣金。</div><p style=\"margin-left: 40px; font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">i) 現金</p><p style=\"margin-left: 40px; font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">ii) 支票</p><p style=\"margin-left: 40px; font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">iii) 信用卡</p><p style=\"margin-left: 40px; font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">接受的信用卡包括VISA、MASTERCARD或CUP。若以信用卡付款，買家須支付額外2%作手續費。買家宜於購買拍品前知會有關信用卡公司，以減少付款時因授權問題而引起的延誤。</p><p style=\"margin-left: 40px; font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">iv) EPS&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-left: 40px; font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">若以EPS付款，買家須支付額外1%作手續費。(上限為港幣5萬元正)</p><p style=\"margin-left: 40px; font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">v) 銀行轉帳</p><p style=\"margin-left: 40px; font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">vi) 銀行匯款</p><p style=\"margin-left: 40px; font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">銀行名稱 :香港上海匯豐銀行有限公司<br></span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">銀行地址 :香港中環皇后大道中1號<br></span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">匯款代碼 :HSBCHKHHHKH<br></span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">收款人 :仕宏拍賣有限公司<br></span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">銀行編號 :004<br></span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">銀行戶口號碼 :053-422283-838</span></p><div style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">若以支票，銀行轉帳或銀行匯款方式付款，須待銀行過帳確認後方可提貨。</span></span></div><div style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp;</div><div style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">如買家未能在30個工作天內支付拍品相關款項，L&amp;H Auction 可向買家收取相關款項的18%作為年利息，並執行以下一項或多項不與法律抵觸的補救措施:</div><div style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp;</div><p style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">i) 對買家提出訴訟，索取違約賠償，包括訴訟費和律師費，及因買家遲付或拒絕付款而造成的利益損失。</p><p style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">ii) 撤銷拍品的出售權或出售給買家的其他拍品，買家仍須支付拍賣佣金。</p><p style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">iii) 重新拍賣該拍品或私下出售，並提出訴訟以索償以下各項差額 :</p><ul style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><li>買家所欠的全部款項、訴訟費和律師費。</li><li>支付所有費用後的再售淨收益，並將盈餘（ 如有 ）付給貨主。</li></ul><p style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">iv) 保管拍品，只有當買家支付全部款項（包括買家佣金） 、所有直接和間接存倉費用及利息後才把拍品交付買家。</p><p style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">v) 保留在拍賣會上出售給該買家的其它拍品。</p><p style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 26, 29);\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">13.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;運輸及提貨</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0.15pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">買家支付所有款項後，可到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">L&amp;H Auction&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">指定地址提貨。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">L&amp;H Auction&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">亦可為買家安排運送服務，買家須承擔運輸費用（包括包裝、運輸及其他相關費用</span><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif; background: rgb(252, 252, 252);\">）</span><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">L&amp;H Auction</span><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">不會承擔運輸過程中所引致的清關、損毀及</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;/&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">或遺失等問題及風險。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">L&amp;H Auction&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">會以買家名義，為寄出的拍品購買全額保險；運輸過程中的保險費、運輸費、包裝費及進出口稅項等將由買家支付。買家須自行索取任何有關拍品進出口、瀕臨絕種生物或其他方面之許可證。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0.15pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">未獲得及</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;/&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">或延誤取得該許可證，均不會被視為買家取消購買或延遲付款的理由。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">L&amp;H Auction&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">不會承擔因未能填妥或呈交所需進出口貨單、清單或其他文件所引致的責任。如買家要求</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">L&amp;H Auction&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">代為申請出口許可證，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">L&amp;H Auction&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">有權就此服務另行收取費用。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">L&amp;H Auction&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">不能保證出口許可證將獲發放。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">L&amp;H Auction&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">及賣家概無就拍品是否就進出口限制及</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;/&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">或禁運作出聲明或保證。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0.15pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">提貨地址</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;:&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">香港銅鑼灣告士打道</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">311</span><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">號皇室堡</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">樓</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1025-29</span><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">室</span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0.15pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">辦公時間</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;:&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">早上</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">時正至晚上</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">時</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">分</span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0.15pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">電話</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;:&nbsp; 852 3907-0282</span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0.15pt;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 26, 29);\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">14.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;有限責任</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0.15pt;\">i)	在任何情況下，本公司及 / 或寄售人的責任，將不會超過該拍品的實際購買價。</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0.15pt;\">ii)	L&amp;H Auction 純粹代表寄售人的權益行事。L&amp;H Auction 會在拍賣會上以買家所出的最高價格出售該拍品，而L&amp;H Auction 並不會就買家提供任何競投意見。如寄售人及 / 或買家違約，L&amp;H Auction 概不負責。</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0.15pt;\">iii)	L&amp;H Auction 不會對此圖錄中的遺漏及 / 或錯誤負上任何責任。如往後他人以此圖錄的資料作其他用途，L&amp;H Auction 將不會承擔任何責任。此外，如需使用或更改本圖錄中內容，需以書面通知L&amp;H Auction 並得到許可方可使用。</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0.15pt;\"><br><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 26, 29);\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">15.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;附帶條款</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0.15pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">本拍賣會中的競投者，均知悉並同意以下條款</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;:</span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0.15pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">i)<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\">L&amp;H Auction&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">有權在本拍賣會開始前或進行期間，以口頭或書面形式更改競投者通知書及一般銷售說</span><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">明及條款。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0.15pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent: -14.7pt; font-size: 13px;\">ii)<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: -14.7pt; font-size: 13px; font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">競投者通知書及一般銷售說明及條款內的交易及相關內容，均根據香港特別行政區的法律解釋和管轄。</span>&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><em><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 0, 0);\"><a href=\"http://www.lhauction.com.hk/tc/notice_to_bidders.php\" _fcksavedurl=\"http://www.lhauction.com.hk/tc/notice_to_bidders.php\">按此閱讀競投者通知書</a></span></em></h3><div><em><br></em></div>', '', ''), ('2', '參與拍賣1', 'BUYING1', '', '            <div class=\"up\"><br></div><div class=\"down\"><div class=\"wsjt\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"block\">\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n\n                </div>\n            </div>\n', '            <div class=\"up\"><br></div><div class=\"down\"><div class=\"wsjt\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"block\">\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n\n                </div>\n            </div>\n', '', ''), ('3', '委託拍賣', 'SELLING', 'http://dev.curio.com/public/static_page/img/152991560957myzxg9.jpg', '              <div class=\"content\">\n                  <p>In order to showcase a wide array of prestigious collections, we are now accepting consignments for the forthcoming L&amp;H Auctions .\n\nWe accept consignments of items under the following categories. If the category of the item you wish to consign is not listed below, please kindly contact us for further discussion. </p>\n                  <div class=\"proj\">\n                      <table style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; height: 65px;    border-top-width: 1px;\n    border-right-width: 1px;\n    border-bottom-width: 1px;\n    border-left-width: 1px;\" border=\"1\" width=\"599\" cellspacing=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\">\n                          <tbody>\n                              <tr>\n                                  <td><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 26, 29);\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Vintage Pu-er Tea</span></span></span></td>\n                                  <td><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 26, 29);\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Classical Chinese Paintings</span></span></span></td>\n                              </tr>\n                              <tr>\n                                  <td><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 26, 29);\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Japanese Teawares &amp; Vessels</span></span></span></td>\n                                  <td><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 26, 29);\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Agarwood &amp; Qinan</span></span></span></td>\n                              </tr>\n                              <tr>\n                                  <td><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 26, 29);\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Celebrity\'s Correspondence &amp; Manuscripts</span></span></span></td>\n                                  <td><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 26, 29);\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Ceramics &amp; Other Chinese Works of Art</span></span></span></td>\n                              </tr>\n                          </tbody>\n                      </table>\n                  </div>\n                  <p>Since the consignment applications were brisk in past auctions, please contact us now with product description and pictures by email to auction@lh-hk.com, together with you contact information such as name, contact number and email.\n\nPlease also read our Auction Consignment Agreement or call us at +852-3168 2192 for further information. </p>\n              </div>\n          \n', '<div class=\"tit\"><span>徵集日程</span></div>\n              <div class=\"date\"><span>馬來西亞吉隆坡站 – 2017年12月8日-12日</span><br><span>中國深圳站 – 2017年12月14日-18日</span><br><span class=\"tips\">更多行程敬請關注仕宏拍賣官方網站或微信公眾號</span></div>\n              <div class=\"content\">\n                  <div class=\"proj\">徵集項目：<br>古董名茶 | 茶具花器 | 中國書畫 | 名人手跡 | 古董珍玩 | 沉香奇楠 |</div>\n                  <p>仕宏拍賣自2013年成立至今，成為香港藏茶界知名的專業古董名茶葉拍賣公司，曾創下以逾1,000萬港元成交一筒百年藍標宋聘圓茶的紀錄；於2017年春季拍賣之古董級普洱茶專場總成交價破3,800萬港元，為茶葉拍賣市場立下彪炳紀錄。希望藉本次現場徵集活動，與藏家增進溝通，推廣茶文化至全球各地。\n我們的專家團隊將會為您提供免費的估值服務。\n\n如欲參與或透過微信或電郵委託拍賣或諮詢，歡迎將委託拍賣珍藏品的資料、新舊狀況及相關圖片，連同個人聯絡資料（姓名、聯絡電話、電郵、微信號等）電郵至 auction@lh-hk.com ，或直接致電+852-3168 2192 / +86 158 1858 1118 洽談委託拍賣事宜，仕宏拍賣專家會為您提供免費估價及市場諮詢服務，歡迎廣大藏家踴躍參與。\n\n賣家亦可參閱拍賣目錄內的拍賣品委託合約或致電+852 3168 2192查詢有關詳情。</p>\n              </div>', null, null), ('4', '公司簡介', 'COMPANY PROFILE', 'http://dev.curio.com/public/static_page/img/1529916343n9em6fwv.png', '<div class=\"tit\">\n                    About L&H Auction Co., Ltd.\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"txt\">\n                    <p>\nEstablished in 2013, L&H Auction Co. Ltd. is a young yet fast-growing auctioneer based in Hong Kong. Its objective is to showcase a variety of antique items and prized collections to the wide public. L&H values fine objects from every culture and time period and strives to provide extraordinary services and opportunities for clients.<br><br>L&H held its first photographical auction in June 2013, focusing on the world’s rarest and finest antique cameras, the famous German Leica. During Spring Auction 2014, L&H has achieved a total of over HK$39 millions. Recording great successes in consecutive sales, L&H has soon become one of the most important auctioneers of vintage cameras in the world.<br><br>Witnessing the immense demand from collectors and antique lovers, L&H has developed its interest to other extensive specialty areas with connoisseurship and professionalism, including but not limited to Vintage Pu-er Tea, Classical Chinese Paintings, Agarwood and Qinan, Japanese Tea wares and Vessels, Wine and Spirits, Ceramics and other Chinese works of art. It created a record of HK$10 million for a tong of 100-year “Song Pin Hao” pu-er tea cake; and achieved a remarkable record of HK$38 million in the tea auction of Spring Auction 2017. While providing professional auction services, L&H actively fosters the cultural development and awareness. With the principle of “High Quality, High Value, High Integrity”, L&H offers high-quality collection and international expertise to create a unique platform for different collectors.<br><br>L&H holds 2 large-scale auctions in Hong Kong every year. Apart from inviting auctions, bids by phone, letters, faxes, and e-mails, bidders can also watch live broadcasts and participate in simultaneous auctions all over the world.\n                    </p>\n                </div>', '                <div class=\"tit\">\n                    關於仕宏拍賣有限公司\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"txt\">\n                    <p>以香港為基地的仕宏拍賣有限公司成立於2013年，秉承「仕以高品而宏」之專業態度及宗旨，力求為收藏興趣愈益多元化的藏家們提供炙手可熱的藏品，將旗下拍賣活動打造成為收藏家們搜尋頂級珍品的良機盛會。<br><br>作為亞洲區舉辦專業相機拍賣的先鋒及佼佼者，仕宏第三屆珍稀相機拍賣會總成交額逾3,900萬港元，在短短兩年間已躍升為全球同類專門相機拍賣行的第二位。<br><br>於2014年開始更引入中國書畫、奇楠沉香、古董普洱名茶及御器等專場拍賣，成為香港藏茶界知名的專業古董名茶葉拍賣公司，曾創下以逾1,000萬港元成交一筒百年藍標宋聘圓茶的紀錄；於2017年春季拍賣之古董級普洱茶專場總成交價破3,800萬港元，為茶葉拍賣市場立下彪炳紀錄。在提供專業拍賣服務的同時，也積極投身於相關文化的發展及傳播中。以多層次的管道向大中華地區提供優質藏品及國際尖端資訊，遵循「高品質，高品味，高誠信度」的服務原則，為廣大藏家打造「可宏高仕之志」的不二平臺。<br><br><br>仕宏拍賣每年於香港舉行2次大型拍賣會，除親臨拍賣會場、電話競投及信件、傳真、電子郵件委託競投外，競投者亦可在世界各地於網上同步參與競投。</p>\n                </div>', null, null), ('5', '競投者通知書', 'Notice to Bidders', '', '<h3 style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><a href=\"./terms_and_condition\"><em><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 0, 0);\">Click here to read Terms And Conditions Of Sale</span></em></a></h3>\n\n<div class=\"t_and_c_title\">&nbsp;</div>\n<p>Please refer to Chinese site.</p>\n<div class=\"t_and_c_info\">\n<h1>&nbsp;</h1>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>						<div class=\"title\" style=\"padding-top:20px;\">Glossary</div>\n						<div class=\"t_and_c_title\"><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 26, 29);\"><strong>Auction:</strong></span></div>\n<div class=\"t_and_c_info\">The auction to be held on 28 May 2017&nbsp;at The Residence, Mezzanine Level, Grand Hyatt<span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp;Hong Kong, 1 Harbour Road, Wan Chai, Hong Kong.</span></div>\n<div class=\"t_and_c_info\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"t_and_c_title\"><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 26, 29);\"><strong>Lot(s):</strong></span></div>\n<div class=\"t_and_c_info\">Any item consigned to L&amp;H Auction that to be available to sales at the Auction.  A lot can be an individual item or items comprised in a group of two or more items offered for sale as one lot.</div>\n<div class=\"t_and_c_info\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"t_and_c_title\"><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 26, 29);\"><strong>Reserve Price:</strong></span></div>\n<div class=\"t_and_c_info\">The minimum price that a Lot may be sold whether by auction or by private treaty.</div>\n<div class=\"t_and_c_info\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"t_and_c_title\"><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 26, 29);\"><strong>Consignor:</strong></span></div>\n<div class=\"t_and_c_info\">A person or a company consign the Lot(s) to be sold in the Auction.</div>\n<div class=\"t_and_c_info\">&nbs